data.description: Check out this charming 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home located in The Oaks of Landis. This home features new vinyl plank flooring on the main level, creating a modern and stylish atmosphere. The first floor boasts a spacious living room, dining room, and kitchen with a large island, perfect for entertaining guests. Additionally, there is an office space, providing a convenient area for work or study. Upstairs, you will find the luxurious owners suite, along with two additional bedrooms, a laundry room, and a versatile loft area. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home!
